name: Jordan Bunniie - Lamp
description:
I SHOOT COLOR TOO! :)
I only got to shoot Jordan Bunniie one time when we both just happened to be in Sacramento at the same time. She was nice enough to shoot with me after she had already spent a full day modeling for a group shoot. She's a badass and a total sweetheart! 

Anyway, still my first day exploring NFTs, and I'm still figuring it out but I have high hopes for what I'm seeing so far. I'm not very good at selling myself or doing work for other people so I've always struggled a bit financially. It's worth it to get to shoot what I want when I want. I'm hoping to finally find a home for my work where people appreciate it so please take a look at the rest of my creations and feel free to contact me at the links in my bio if you have any questions.
